commit.message:
86numaux.adb, [...]: Add 2001 to copyright notice.

	* 86numaux.adb, a-tigeau.ads, a-wtgeau.ads, fname-sf.ads, g-traceb.ads,
	s-tasdeb.ads, sem_maps.ads: Add 2001 to copyright notice.

From-SVN: r46658

@@ -118,7 +118,6 @@ package body Ada.Numerics.Aux is
    --  reduction of the argument is done for arguments in the range of
    --  -2.0**63 .. 2.0**63, using a 66-bit approximation of Pi.
 
-
    pragma Inline (Is_Nan);
    pragma Inline (Reduce);

@@ -1,3 +1,8 @@
+2001-10-30  Geert Bosch <bosch@gnat.com>
+
